* Paul Romanko: [[Bass guitar|bass]] (1996<U+2013>present)
* [[Jason Bittner]]: [[Drum kit|drums]], [[Percussion instrument|percussion]] (2000<U+2013>present)

=== Former members ===

* [[Adam Dutkiewicz]]: session drums (1996)
* [[Philip Labonte]]: vocals (1996<U+2013>1999)
* David Germain: drums (1996<U+2013>2000)

